# Banana Claims - Current Status

## Project
Banana Claims is a server-side Fabric land claim mod.

## Development Rules
- Provide complete replacement files only.
- One feature per commit.
- Every feature must compile before moving on.
- Every feature must be tested in-game before moving on.
- Keep development focused and fast.

## Completed Features
- /claim
- /claim create <name>
- /claim info
- /claim list
- /claim delete
- /claim rename <newName>
- /claim description <text>
- Claim model
- ClaimManager
- ClaimChunk
- ClaimStorage
- JSON persistence
- Ownership checks for modifying claims

## Current State
The core claim command system is working and persistent.
Claims save to config/bananaclaims/claims.json and reload after server restart.

## Next Feature
Enter/leave popup system.